Package: phylosophy
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2020-02-19
Title: phylosophy
Authors@R: c(
    person("Vinh", "Tran", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "tran@bio.uni-frankfurt.de"))
Description: PhyloProfile is a toolkit for generating and exploring complex phylogenetic profiles. It provides solutions for searching orthologs for a set of genes of interest, enhancing the functional linkages between query genes and their orthologs with feature similarity scores, and finally visually exploring the phylogenetic profiles of query genes.
URL: https://github.com/BIONF/phylosophy/
